Enable biome linter to Ignore files or folders:

One must follow this pattern in `biome.json`:
```
 "files": {
    "includes": [
      "**/*.js",
      "**/*.jsx",
      "**/*.ts",
      "**/*.tsx",
      "!**/.cursor/**", // ignored rules 
      "!**/.next/**", // ignored rules
      "!**/node_modules/**" // ignored rules
    ]
  }
  // ...
```

Do NOT attempt ignore rules inside "overrides.include"!


